Package: geonapi
Type: Package
Title: GeoNetwork REST API R Interface
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2017-07-03
Authors@R: c(person("Emmanuel", "Blondel", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "emmanuel.blondel1@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5870-5762")))
Maintainer: Emmanuel Blondel <emmanuel.blondel1@gmail.com>
Description: Provides an R interface to the GeoNetwork REST API, allowing to upload 
 and publish metadata in a GeoNetwork web-application and expose it to OGC Web-Services.
 (Catalogue Service for the Web).
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), geometa
Imports: R6, openssl, httr, XML
Suggests: testthat, roxygen2
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/eblondel/geonapi/wiki, http://geonetwork-opensource.org
BugReports: https://github.com/eblondel/geonapi/issues
LazyLoad: yes
